{"tid":39952,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"美籍廚師鑚研熟成壽司　腐壞前最鮮美","createTime":"2016-12-15T01:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T15:01:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a51181efe3d26e068dac1491c2413c7f41e618","tid":39952,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20161215/org/1481726100_d0d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20161215%2Forg%2F1481726100_d0d5.jpg&h=f696f853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2016/12/14/3231393/20161215_Vvvsub12new_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F3231393%2F20161215_Vvvsub12new_clean_w.mp4&d=iLkuKafLdiqbu189Z6HAA3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=9bf3a541\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2016/12/14/3231393/20161215_Vvvsub12new_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20161215/large/15fb606p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20161215%2Flarge%2F15fb606p.jpg&h=fe5b568d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Okra大廚Max Levy來自美國新奧爾良，師承日本名廚安田直道。 <br />\n <br />\n「熟成壽司」近年開始為港人所認識，但未算普及。大家相信它比「鮮」魚更佳嗎？這次就由擅長製作「熟成壽司」的美籍大廚Max Levy給我們解答：「新鮮上碟又是否最好的享用方法？」 <br />\n <br />\n來到香港，熟成壽司絕不常見，而西營盤的Okra Sushi Bar，最近就大膽在Omakase餐牌中以熟成壽司作重要菜式。來自美國新奧爾良的餐廳大廚Max Levy，師承在東京和紐約都有壽司店的名廚安田直道，他既有日廚好手勢，亦有外國人的大膽實驗精神。他自2004年開始醉心鑽研熟成魚技術，每天將當造魚清洗後放入雪櫃存放，定期取出置於室溫，浸泡於鹽水中一段時間後再重新冷藏，每次的溫度、濕度、時間等都會影響成品。Max解釋說：「酵素會分解魚的膠原及細胞結構，越熟成得久，肉質會越軟，所以脂肪豐富而堅實的魚肉，例如魚腩位置，最能因為熟成而變得美味。」 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20161215/large/15fb607pnew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20161215%2Flarge%2F15fb607pnew.jpg&h=88b1e07f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Omakase（廚師發辦）套餐中，既有新鮮食海產，亦有熟成魚做食材。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20161215/large/15fb610p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20161215%2Flarge%2F15fb610p.jpg&h=62834439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 獨特的Okra Sushi Bar位於Okra餐廳一樓。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20161215/large/15fb609p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20161215%2Flarge%2F15fb609p.jpg&h=21e2995c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n $880 Omakase套餐（包括前菜、10-14件手握壽司、熱盤及甜品）另加$600配4-6款清酒或天然葡萄酒 <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<strong>熟成魚味道更濃郁</strong><br />\nMax強調製作熟成魚沒有秘方、也沒有方程式，所需要是長時間的經驗累積去了解魚肉是「熟成了」，還是「變壞了」，裏頭其實是一線之差，亦需要每天親自試味，直到熟成至他認為客人能接受的味道。熟成魚味道變得更濃郁，所以他配搭的壽司飯混合了新潟越光米及五百萬石米，一香甜一帶嚼勁加強口感，再配多款鹽去調味，味道不搶喉但鮮味非常濃，最適合配上較野性或帶泥味的清酒去品嚐，享受魚鮮真正的鮮味。 <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<strong>熟成壽司推介</strong><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20161215/large/15fb601p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20161215%2Flarge%2F15fb601p.jpg&h=9a3a3b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 分別熟成7天（左）及12天的熟成赤身壽司配竹炭鹽，味道非常獨特。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20161215/large/15fb608p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20161215%2Flarge%2F15fb608p.jpg&h=36998d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 分別熟成10天（左）及3天的熟成大拖羅壽司配鹽漬檸檬皮，肉質非常軟腍，味道亦較一般大拖羅更甘甜。 <br />\n <br />\n <br />\nOkra　西營盤皇后大道西110號一樓 <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n記者：黃穎妮<br />\n攝影：陳健邦、周芝瑩<br />\n編輯：梁浩維<br />\n美術：利英豪 <br />\n <br />\n <br />\nsource : <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2F&d=iLkuKafLdiqbu189Z6HAA3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d2450c8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2F&h=7a93f946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/</a><br />\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++"},{"pid":"73ff0ee7ac4a82708585ff69763af147f54f7c5e","tid":39952,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"Ok,好似唔錯"},{"pid":"1568e453fee7d46804d5046b4b9183fb43094b03","tid":39952,"uid":19272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:44:30.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"84731f85931c865aa7a0e1c917bd6f676e51aa68","tid":39952,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f6e3798b4b31a4f7dd9e502cd3a879b150e6c91","tid":39952,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"有創意 我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de355c412806ad32aabd1783f9eabe0741c4589f","tid":39952,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"中國古代咪有呢d壽c"},{"pid":"398790bae220c4abf1f0a5c9e522adcd21beb4af","tid":39952,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"壽司舊肉好似痴貼紙咁"},{"pid":"0052ab6b6c7003f8dd40f4d43ff6dd9cc4591941","tid":39952,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"其實壽司最開始係用類似熟成魚肉，之後慢慢演變先變到近代咁用魚生"},{"pid":"3bef0cb07c3e71904c121448d8e88d4c3df0bb65","tid":39952,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實壽司最開始係用類似熟成魚肉，之後慢慢演變先變到近代咁用魚生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同米一齊發酵<br />\n之後同果啲米一齊食所以啲米會酸<br />\n<br />\n後來江戶前壽司太受歡迎等唔切發酵就慢慢變左鮮魚"},{"pid":"4f04b683712f81e96ef37790338f6daa57ad403a","tid":39952,"uid":15407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:00:43.000Z","msg":"好似好撚勁咁"},{"pid":"5d357e34f5517dca497b9f7e174eb35802f1781a","tid":39952,"uid":53426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:04:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3a0d998b41492fc97afdfb5144336cf2c26fa26","tid":39952,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:04:57.000Z","msg":"食戟之靈真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幸平熟成秋刀魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1471631e898e3a55b34dd5ee966a0bf1d530a98","tid":39952,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"啲裝修好似公共浴室"},{"pid":"b18364b70069649f0d214bf5ef878ad388a94bd9","tid":39952,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"死的美味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef08ac26648dd338205cf79cbe9229295b23cd88","tid":39952,"uid":5900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"問過明將未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db55526d5fa01c8a077486acc8b12c04d34b4f79","tid":39952,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:25:21.000Z","msg":"咪即係皮蛋嗰類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2adb5e201b22c4aa6f37f98fcb9c0f3b9308e32","tid":39952,"uid":9714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"雖然未試過<br />\n亦未食過<br />\n點都會食新鮮"},{"pid":"866b548ab974242194bfe597f3dde3faec71e51d","tid":39952,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike"